				\begin{document}$$N/\sqrt {{\mathrm{log}}(N)}$$\end{document}N/log(N) as a τ parameter based on a study of simulated and real genomic data. In this study, in addition to the main analysis setting τ equal to \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
